<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到那个奇怪的小女孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>沿着西街蹦蹦跳跳走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啦啦啦啦啦！”小女孩儿唱着歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个小女孩儿把美罗城所有的东西变小的。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在整个城市都消失前，我必须阻止她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西刚飞起来就听到一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喵！一只猫正盯着路边的什么东西看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西低头一看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那些被变小的人！”罗西喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>受惊的小人们吓得到处逃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命啊！”有人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猫要吃掉我们！”另一个人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喵！猫向空中扑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在猫落地之前抓住了它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏猫！”她说，“不可以吃人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把小人们带进了一家披萨店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“待在这里。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上就去阻止这件事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑到外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”一个微弱的声音喊道，“救救我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，还有谁需要帮助呢？”罗西心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬头看到一只老鹰飞过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用她的超级视力看着那只老鹰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哦！”罗西喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只老鹰抓了一个小人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西赶紧飞起来。嗖！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把那个人还给我！”罗西向老鹰喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鹰扔下男人，飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”男人大叫，“我掉下去了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！罗西迅速飞过去，抓住了那个男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西降落的时候，松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！“那是什么？”罗西心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！”一个小声音叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是我才买的车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西低头一看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从她的靴子底下，掉下一辆被踩得粉碎的小车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西再一次飞向天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我得找到那个奇怪的小女孩儿。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在美罗城上方飞着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>找遍了所有的地方，都没有发现那个小女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！”罗西坐在一栋大楼的楼顶上思考着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，嗡！她坐着的大楼开始缩小了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而那个小女孩儿就站在下面的街道上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳离了那栋大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多可爱的小楼啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个小女孩儿咯咯笑着，把大楼放进了口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啦啦啦啦啦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿唱着歌，蹦蹦跳跳走在街上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！”罗西喊道，“你给我站住！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个奇怪的小女孩儿抬头一看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西正向自己飞过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿看起来很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”小女孩儿喊道，“不要啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿用仪器瞄准罗西。嗡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西尖叫道，“我在变小！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>